---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Financial Statements"
  description="Tax Doctor prepares financial statements including balance sheets, income statements, fixed asset schedules and more for businesses in Johannesburg."
  keywords="financial statements, balance sheet, income statement, profit and loss, it14, sars, johannesburg"
>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Financial Statements</h2>
    <p>Financial statements comprise:</p>
    <ul class="alt">
      <li>Directors and Accounting Officer / Auditor reports</li>
      <li>Balance sheet</li>
      <li>Income statement (Profit and Loss)</li>
      <li>Fixed assets schedule</li>
      <li>Cashflows</li>
      <li>Notes to the balance sheet and income statement</li>
    </ul>
    <p>There are many reasons why people need financial statements, for example:</p>
    <ul class="alt">
      <li>Submission to SARS (IT14)</li>
      <li>Management reporting on profit and loss, customers (debtors) / suppliers (creditors), etc.</li>
      <li>Bank loans</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We can provide statements in Excel and/or Quickbooks.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
